# Complete Investigator - Aurora Builder Content

This folder contains an Aurora Builder content package for the Investigator class from Complete Investigator.

Included:
- complete-investigator.index
- source.xml
- classes/class-investigator.xml
- spells.xml
- licenses/OGL-NOTICE.txt

Scope:
- Base Investigator class features through level 20
- Detective occult specialization only
- New spells and spell-list support from Complete Investigator

Hosting:
Replace USERNAME/REPOSITORY/main in complete-investigator.index with your hosted raw GitHub path, then host this folder structure unchanged.

Local use:
You can also copy the XML files into Documents/5e Character Builder/custom/user and reload Aurora.

Notes:
The Ritualist selector includes ritual spells and custom Investigator Ritual spells as a tracking aid. Some official PHB spells are treated as bonus rituals by the class text; if Aurora does not list a bonus PHB spell under the selector, add it manually according to the class feature text.
